which Zhan Yan will also attend.

75
00:03:45,440 --> 00:03:46,410
By the time,

76
00:03:46,490 --> 00:03:47,280
the two of you

77
00:03:47,560 --> 00:03:48,250
can have some time alone.

78
00:03:48,250 --> 00:03:49,410
