146
00:05:58,690 --> 00:05:59,640
Wasn't I generous before I

147
00:05:59,640 --> 00:06:00,560
turned Associate Chief Physician?

148
00:06:01,170 --> 00:06:02,250
I just want you to

149
00:06:02,250 --> 00:06:03,170
