00:07:10,370 --> 00:07:11,250
Can you drop coattails?

201
00:07:11,250 --> 00:07:12,050
Here.

202
00:07:12,730 --> 00:07:13,250
Why hasn't Dr. Cai

203
00:07:13,250 --> 00:07:14,400
