223
00:07:40,490 --> 00:07:41,690
Let me walk you out.

224
00:07:46,690 --> 00:07:48,320
They're really boisterous.

225
00:07:48,690 --> 00:07:49,320
I know

226
00:07:49,320 --> 00:07:50,490
