251
00:08:47,400 --> 00:08:48,130
OK.

252
00:08:48,800 --> 00:08:49,680
Let me open the door.

253
00:08:51,970 --> 00:08:52,970
Go back.

254
00:08:53,370 --> 00:08:53,970
OK.

255
00:08:54,330 --> 00:08:55,090
Bye.

256
00:08:55,490 --> 00:08:56,250
Bye.

